      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine is incredibly responsive, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature works exactly as intended. It has a complete service history and has always been garaged, making it an ideal choice for a collector or a buyer who demands the absolute best. You can expect a driving experience that feels identical to a brand-new vehicle.",
